<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح:</span> خ <span class="c2">(١٨٧٥)</span>، م <span class="c2">(٤/ ١٢٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الشَّيْخُ:</span> يَبُسُّون أَيْ: يَنسِلُونَ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>